additionalProperty.value: INGREDIENTS: Vine Fruits (36.5%) (Sultanas, Raisins, Currants), Sugar, Brandy (9%), Cider (8.5%) (Preservative (224)), Non Hydrogenated Vegetable Oil (Palm Oil**, Rice Flour, Sunflower Oil), Breadcrumb (Wheat Flour, Salt, Yeast), Wheat Flour, Humectant (422), Port (Preservative (Sulphur Dioxide)), Candied Mixed Peel (Orange Peel, Glucose-fructose Syrup, Lemon Peel, Sugar, Acidity Regulator (330), Preservative (Sulphur Dioxide)), Treacle, Orange Juice from Concentrate, Molasses, Mixed Spice, Salt, Orange Oil.Contains 1.5mL alcohol per 100g pudding.
